I"s<h2 id="adobe-creative-jam--airbnb">Adobe Creative Jam + Airbnb</h2>

<p>Adobe teamed up with Airbnb to foster design thinking, and show off new talent. They held a nation wide competition in 2020 to see how we could create new ways for friends and family to travel together and share photos when booking through Airbnb and using Adobeâ€™s new Prototyping software, XD.</p>

<h2 id="iterations">Iterations</h2>

<p>Due to the quick 48 hour turn around time we had during this Creative Jam, our team did not go through many iterations. We focused on laying out components in the interface that would make sense to the viewer before focusing on a solid design direction.</p>

