<h2 id="relive-edit-and-share-your-picture-perfect-moments">Relive, edit, and share your picture-perfect moments.</h2>

<p>Moments is where you can upload all the amazing photos you take on your trip. Keep everyone up to date on your latest activites and sights. Posting your travel photos and video clips to the shared cloud photo album brings the memories together.</p>
